Welcome to News &amp; Facts!  In these pages you will find a wide range of  information regarding Bankers Trust, including our <a href="profile/index.html">Corporate Profile</a>, an introduction to <a href="/cgi-bin/isg/nph-form?FormId=setbtab&topleft=banners/flag.html&bottomleft=menu.html&size=20&topright=banners/b-alexb.html&bottomright=home/home.html">BT Alex. Brown</a>  and our most recent <a href="finhigh/index.html">Quarterly Financial Highlights</a>. Also, for a description of Bankers Trust's offices around the globe, you can take a look at <a href="country/map.html">Bankers Trust Worldwide</a>.<P>



